Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:46.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter! And snow-covered mountains mean skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And my long-awaited boy-hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:54.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, there's only 5 or 6 guys on the slopes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're all with their girlfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the place really is empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:03.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only untaken guy here is Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yeah, yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, let's just have fun skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:11.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for you since you have Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:16.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried my hardest these past 17 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing good has ever happened to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can pay for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:32.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to ski with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Kittens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ski instructors. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0} and Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you! Good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:53.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You know these girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:58.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They were students of mine when I taught at Teitan Elementary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh yeah, I remember a teacher like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you two sure have grown womanly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, you're as stunning as ever with that long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just my hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:13.61,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)\pos(440,320)}Akiko Yonehara (30)\NHaido Elementary Teacher\N(Ran and Sonoko's former teacher)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the 30 year old woman who could never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what about these nice instructor friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructors, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Grade school teachers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you both work with Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0} at Haido Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They're my coworkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.42,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(174,350)}Kohei Shimoda (30)\NHaido Elementary Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher for Class 5-1, Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and boys P.E. instructor, Sakai-{\i1}sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.55,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(274,350)}Ryuichi Sakai (29)\NHaido Elementary P.E. Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:50.52,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(316,350)}Minori Nakamura (27)\NHaido Elementary Health Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, grade school teachers trying to pick up high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are still so young at heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody uses "kittens" nowadays!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he be? Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A music teacher who wound up coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed to meet here at 2:00, but he's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose he went on ahead to the lodge we're staying at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so he can scare us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very possible. He loves that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come to the lodge, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! No seducing my students!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:33.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We'll drive 'em back in time for their ski bus home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:38.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure this is the road?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:47.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me! Are there any lodges around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's one halfway up that mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't tell me you're goin' up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This area gets pounded by blizzards every evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} might be waiting for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Who booked us out here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me. Wasn't it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was it Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:28.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,40)\a6\fs24}Annual (Secret) Ski Tour\N2 Days 1 Night\NSet for December 21\N \NWill Attend   Will Not Attend\NPlease Circle Selection\N \NLocation & Members To Be\NKept Secret Until Just\NBefore The Event ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:27.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did what that card I found in my desk two weeks ago said to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and circled that I would attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:34.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You usually organize our trips,\Nso I thought you did this one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:39.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Plus, there was another note\Nin my desk yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A list of the attendees and a map to the meeting place and lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:48.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one, too! Who could've put them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the person with the key to the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone here must have gotten it from the lodge's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:06:01.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the key. I found it in my desk yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who rented the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me. Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} called me last night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and told me to get a rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wasn't he the one who planned all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what're you doing? Let's go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cold out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A fireplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad we came, Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can leave in this blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll phone your parents,\Nso stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it really OK to rent such a fancy lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} pay,\Nsince he planned this tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's our sponsor, Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for taking so long, Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:15.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:22.48,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,340)}Atsushi Mori (37)\NNewspaper Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:22.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a newshound who these folks really helped out three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a tip-off that something's gonna happen here tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:31.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Something's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}gonna happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:40.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I parked in the forest and waited for you\Nwhen a blizzard suddenly hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:47.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wise? I'll just write,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:55.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Haido Elementary Teacher Throws Reporter Out Into Blizzard."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0} and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Everyone suddenly stopped talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were having so much fun.\NThat guy ruined it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:13.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him and\Nhelp me make everyone's beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:20.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two can help Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0} with dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, has Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} called or anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:32.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I got his machine at home, so I think he's on his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You do that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0} isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong, Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher! Say something, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}"Mi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(312,430)\fs24\b0\fnShinGoPro-Medium}ミ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko! What's going on?! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:35.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:38.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the commotion here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:54.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Someone attacked you?! Honestly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone covered my mouth from behind\Nwhile I was making the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I felt faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:06.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this handkerchief? People on TV do it a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,knocking someone out with\Na handkerchief soaked in chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was strangled with it after she was knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There are rope marks on her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you strangled, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put up a fight, but I don't know what happened after I passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:35.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I even had my head bashed into the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"{\i1}Mi{\i0}"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:52.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My lipstick is gone! I had it in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's some on Sonoko's hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one says, "Na..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(398,430)\fs24\blur2\b0\fnShinGoPro-Medium}ナ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi" and "na"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,430)\blur2\fs24}minagoroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A massacre?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:10.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the culprit is trying to tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing nobody died, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:18.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you won't have to bend the truth\Nlike you did three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:22.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already! Are you still stuck on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I bet you attacked them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:32.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in front of the fireplace when that girl screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:37.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, is it really a good idea\Nto have a brat chase the culprit alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Perfect! There are still tracks here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If I follow these...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The front door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait! That means the attacker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:58.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have inhaled too much chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll wake up soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, was the stuff about the footprints true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They went from the window to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But who says the attacker made them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan kicked the door down 'cause it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That door only locks from the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the window was the only way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the attacker might've taken refuge inside the lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:39.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! That jerk did all this to scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:44.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious! Myself aside, Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0} has been strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much to be a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:54.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, what could Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0} be thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he'd show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:13:01.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he can't come out now that it's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you when there were two women being attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:09.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me. I was takin' a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in my room listening to music on my headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you watch Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets attacked again, bust out your karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s shoes are wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0}. Where were you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:34.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't in the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the gas wasn't coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:40.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went out the back to check the gas tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, where's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little more. It's cooking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish making the beds until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go check on dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to filch some food, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for making me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. There was an extra helping, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:10.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'll never forget what happened three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:15.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's this "three years ago" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:18.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry about it, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Those two didn't eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:24.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said they'll eat when Sonoko-{\i1}chan{\i0} wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. We sure have inconvenienced her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Sugiyama! We know you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:41.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sneaking around and get out... Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're all right. The heater's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the lodge's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was snowing, so he was worried if the heater was working or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}How odd. There's definitely something going on in this lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Looks like I'll need to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:03.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}First is the incident three years ago\Neverybody's tight-lipped about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm sure I brought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc's Earring Cell Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Doc's number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.00,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,350)}Dr. Agasa's Home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:23.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? An incident at Haido Elementary three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:30.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be case files in my dad's study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:33.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry! I got a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, someone else might...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you, Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The music teacher has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya doin'? Come inside already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?! Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he froze to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This man was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:27.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See this rope mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:34.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the body's stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that called rigor mortis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that means he was killed over 9 hours ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:50.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that his body rang the bell means someone set him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:55.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we were all eating by the fireplace when it rang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the killer isn't one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the one who attacked Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0} and Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the "ko" on his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,430)\blur2\fs24\b0\fnShinGoPro-Medium}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:14.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a letter written in lipstick just like they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:19.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0} had "mi" and Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0} had "na", which makes:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"{\i1}Mi-na-ko{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got nothing to do with it! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! It's Yonehara! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until he cools down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:48.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:55.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we found Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s body leaning by the front door...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:02.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They could've snuck inside while we were all gathered at the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:07.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Sakai-{\i1}sensei{\i0} is calling the police as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's too dangerous to send cars in the blizzard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:15.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we gotta wait until it dies down in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:20.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they want us to sit here until morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the killer could still be inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all this have to happen? It was such a fun ski tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he were here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:31.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Shin'ichi! Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"School Lunch Money"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who found everyone's lunch money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I lost it in 4th grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:48.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that cheeky runt from the class next door who acted like a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Excuse me for being cheeky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a high school detective now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I did see him in the papers. I think his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:05.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A brilliant 16 year old detective who handled unsolvable cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:10.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty good for a kid, so I was gonna do a feature on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's been no word on him lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it he croaked after poking his nose into some case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! Shin'ichi is ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to warn you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to not take your eyes off that guy holed up in his room upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:37.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my reporter's instinct is right,\Nhe'll be next to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:44.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the more casualties, the better the article and the better for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. The upstairs windows don't open,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he won't get attacked if he's holed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he is a bit agitated.\NIt's dangerous to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give him some coffee to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:06.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0} and I will make some,\Nso you go be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:12.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be extra careful! The killer could be hiding inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm dead! I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someone's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}! Coffee and cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}An outside job... Or was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}When the doorbell rang, everyone was together but Ran and Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:43.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so it was definitely someone else\Nwho placed the body here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Huh? Only that part of the railing is missing snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Did someone get on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:53.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What's with that groove?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's one on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Could this have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you shouldn't wander around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room and get in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\blur2}Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:10.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0} won't let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's leave him alone, lock our rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and get some rest until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doc. Figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.58,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes, I finally found the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:33.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, a girl hanged herself in the volleyball room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at Haido Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.60,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the cause was "exam neurosis."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the blame was focused on her teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the teacher's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:48.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not listed here, but the girl's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:52.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haido Elementary, Class 6-2, Minako Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Minako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mention anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:58.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing there, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.43,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:04.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's the Doc. Is this a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.30,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hey, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shin'ichi there, Doc?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:18.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Upstairs... Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:24:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(134,104)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:45.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:46.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:48.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:55.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Not here! Not here! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:24:01.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If it's not hidden anywhere,\Nthat means the killer still has the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:03.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}One of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer... is you!
