Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:14.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,123)\a2\fscx90\fscy90\fnDINk\c&HFFFFFF&\b0\fs36\bord0\shad0}The Ski Lodge Murder Case
