Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:19.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Hair
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:19.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,314)\b0\fnLos Altos II\c&H00&\bord0\shad0}Hair
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,410)\1a&H1F&\fnSegoe\3c&H7F001F&\3a&H7F&\fscx100\bord2\shad0\fs28}Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, it's the first Conan of the new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Christmas, New Ye—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:23.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Figure out the killer yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:24.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yikes, uh-oh.
